OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FThe impacts of the war in Iran are
OL,10,Fwide-ranging, and the latest industry
OL,11,Fto really feel its effects is aviation.
OL,13,FIran has used its control over part of
OL,14,Fthe Strait of Hormuz to prevent
OL,15,Fvessels from travelling through the
OL,16,Fpassage, creating a chokepoint for
OL,17,Fhuge quantities of oil and gas
OL,18,Fsupplies. Oil and gas markets have
OL,19,Fsubsequently been sent into turmoil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FFuel is an airline's highest operating
OL,7,Fcost, so as oil prices surge and the
OL,8,Fpossibility of shortages looms,
OL,9,Fcompanies have to work out how to
OL,10,Fweather the storm, without knowing how
OL,11,Flong it could last.
OL,13,FAs oil prices continue to rise, ITV
OL,14,FNews explains what the aviation sector
OL,15,Fdoes now.
OL,17,FWill flights be cancelled?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FWhile some airlines have already
OL,7,Fcancelled flights to specific
OL,8,Fdestinations, such as Tel Aviv, due to
OL,9,Ftheir geographical proximity to the
OL,10,FIran conflict, others have started
OL,11,Fcancelling flights because of fuel
OL,12,Fissues.
OL,14,FThe chief executive of Ryanair, for
OL,15,Fexample, has said the airline will not
OL,16,Fbe able to run its full summer
OL,17,Fschedule because of jet fuel shortages
OL,18,Fif the Strait of Hormuz continues to
OL,19,Fremain closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,F"The Strait of Hormuz has been closed
OL,7,Ffor 30 days. If it remains closed for
OL,8,F60 or 90 days, then we're all facing
OL,9,Fan unknown scenario, and we are
OL,10,Fcertainly looking at maybe having to
OL,11,Fcancel 5%`10% of flights through May,
OL,12,FJune and July," Michael O'Leary told
OL,13,FITV News on Thursday.
OL,15,FBut he did insist that most flights
OL,16,Fwill operate and warned that delaying
OL,17,Fbooking is more likely to result in
OL,18,Fpaying higher prices as airfares rise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
