OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FFurther cancellations across the
OL,12,Fsector could come, according to James
OL,13,FKelly, Head of Aviation Finance at
OL,14,FKPMG Ireland, who said: "Airlines
OL,15,Fmight seek to trim unprofitable routes
OL,16,Ffrom their network."
OL,18,FWhich flights could be cancelled?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
