OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FMr O'Leary said that airlines won't be
OL,7,Fable to choose which routes to cancel
OL,8,F- cuts will depend on which airports
OL,9,Fsuffer fuel shortages.
OL,11,FHe said he expects to have only a few
OL,12,Fdays' notice from jet fuel suppliers
OL,13,Fif there are issues, making disruption
OL,14,Fhard to manage. That could then have a
OL,15,Fknock-on effect for passengers.
OL,17,FA number of airports in Italy -
OL,18,FBologna, Milan Linate, Treviso and
OL,19,FVenice - have already been hit by
OL,20,Frestrictions on aviation fuel,
OL,21,Faccording to local media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FThe Italian branch of Air BP, one of
OL,7,Fthe world's leading suppliers of
OL,8,Faviation fuel, issued a notice to
OL,9,Fairlines (NOTAM) informing them that
OL,10,Ffuel distribution will be rationed
OL,11,Funtil April 9, the reports said, with
OL,12,Fpriority being given to air ambulance
OL,13,Fflights, state flights and flights
OL,14,Flasting more than three hours.
OL,16,FIf they do have the choice, airlines
OL,17,Ftend to prioritise protecting long-
OL,18,Fhaul flights and routes that are in
OL,19,Fhigh demand, so it could be shorter
OL,20,Fflights that aren't as popular that
OL,21,Fcould be first to be cancelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FIf you have booked flights, it is
OL,7,Falways advisable to check with your
OL,8,Fspecific airline before travelling.
OL,10,FWhat have different airlines said?
OL,12,FMr O'Leary said the airline will not
OL,13,Fbe able to run its full summer
OL,14,Fschedule because of jet fuel shortages
OL,15,Fif the Strait of Hormuz remains closed.
OL,17,FThe chief executive said that if the
OL,18,Fwar in Iran doesn't end "by the end of
OL,19,FApril", he expects European airlines
OL,20,Fto start cutting scheduled flights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
