PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FAurigny, which flies from Guernsey to
OL,7,FBirmingham, Bristol, Dublin,
OL,8,FEdinburgh, Exeter, Jersey, Leeds,
OL,9,FLondon, Manchester, Paris and
OL,10,FSouthampton, has said "difficult
OL,11,Fdecisions have had to be made" in
OL,12,Fresponse to the rising fuel prices.
OL,14,F"This includes cancelling certain
OL,15,Fflights between mid-April and June,
OL,16,Fcombining services from nearby UK
OL,17,Fairports to reduce the number of empty
OL,18,Fseats, and the introduction of a
OL,19,Ftemporary fuel surcharge of #2 on all
OL,20,Fbookings made from March 20."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FAll Skybus flights between Cornwall
OL,7,Fand London have been cancelled from
OL,8,FFriday, April 3, because of rising
OL,9,Ffuel costs and a drop in passenger
OL,10,Fnumbers.
OL,12,FThe route from Newquay Airport to
OL,13,FLondon Gatwick was a public service
OL,14,Fobligation funded by Cornwall Council
OL,15,Fand the Department for Transport, but
OL,16,Fit is being pulled two months earlier
OL,17,Fthan expected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FThe service has been operated by
OL,7,FCornwall's Skybus since the previous
OL,8,Foperator, Eastern Airways, went bust
OL,9,Flast November. An agreement with
OL,10,FSkybus was due to end on May 31, but
OL,11,F"economic uncertainty" has halted
OL,12,Fthings earlier than expected.
OL,14,FScandinavian Airlines
OL,16,FScandinavian airline SAS announced in
OL,17,FMarch it would be cancelling around
OL,18,F1,000 flights in March and April as a
OL,19,Fresult of the surge in jet fuel prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
