OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,F"The sharp increase in fuel costs is
OL,7,Faffecting the entire European aviation
OL,8,Fsystem," a spokesperson told The Wall
OL,9,FStreet Journal in March.
OL,11,FWhere do airlines get their jet fuel?
OL,13,FAccording to data analytics firm
OL,14,FKpler, 18.8 million tonnes of jet fuel
OL,15,Fwere shipped out of the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz last year - a little over a
OL,17,Ffifth of total global seaborne exports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FChina - the world's second-largest jet
OL,7,Ffuel producer - is restricting
OL,8,Fexports. South Korea, another key
OL,9,Fproducer, has cut output as it
OL,10,Fstruggles to source crude oil to
OL,11,Frefine.
OL,13,FMore tankers are now bringing jet fuel
OL,14,Ffrom the US to Europe, but the
OL,15,Fquantity does not match the amount
OL,16,Flost.
OL,18,F"Even if the war ends immediately,
OL,19,Fthere's a crunch looming," Michelle
OL,20,FBockmann, a maritime analyst with
OL,21,FWindward, told ITV News.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31014
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FWill flights become more expensive?
OL,8,FA likely knock-on effect of the
OL,9,Fincrease in oil prices is an increase
OL,10,Fin customer costs.
OL,12,F"Airlines cannot afford to bear these
OL,13,Fhigher fuel prices - it is likely that
OL,14,Fthere will be increases in air fares
OL,15,Fin the coming months as airlines pass
OL,16,Fon the higher cost of fuel to their
OL,17,Fcustomers," Mr Kelly said.
OL,19,FCould airlines use less jet fuel?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31015
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775581553
OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FIf the current issues around fuel
OL,7,Fbecome longer term, airlines are
OL,8,Flikely to refocus on modernising their
OL,9,Faircraft fleets, as new technology
OL,10,Faircraft and engines can be 15-20%
OL,11,Fmore fuel efficient than older craft,
OL,12,FMr Kelly says.
OL,14,FBut it's no quick fix.
OL,16,F"Fleet modernisation takes years and
OL,17,Frequires a lot of capital. If you
OL,18,Fordered a new aircraft from Boeing and
OL,19,FAirbus now, it would likely only
OL,20,Fdeliver after 2030!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
