OL,3,CHow will passengers be affected by
OL,4,Cpossible jet fuel shortages?
OL,6,FThe availability of new aircraft had
OL,7,Falready been impacted by post-Covid
OL,8,Fsupply chain issues, the impacts of
OL,9,Fglobal tariffs and quality concerns.
OL,11,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,12,Four political experts are across all
OL,13,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,14,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
